	        </p>
       		<div class="flexcenter">
            	<div class="sbutton" style="width: 100%; padding: 20px; ">
					<button id="aButton" style="cursor: pointer; " onclick="window.location.href='home.jsp'">Back to Home</button>
				</div>
            </div>
        </div>
